<item>
            <title>[LU-13640] Interop: conf-sanity test 125 fails with &apos;test_125 failed with 1&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13640</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Under &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12387&quot; title=&quot;l_tunedisk does not properly handle multipath devices&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-12387&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-12387&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the l_tunedisk utility was modified to recognize and skip tuning MDS and MGS devices. conf-sanity test_125 was added to make sure only OSS devices were tuned. These changes landed prior to the release of 2.12.3. Thus, conf-sanity test 125 should be skipped for all servers with version less than 2.12.3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&#8217;ve seen this test fail for 2.12.x client and 2.10.y server testing:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/897de78c-d22b-11e9-98c8-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/897de78c-d22b-11e9-98c8-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ba24f6bd-817d-4c29-8901-a40467d24211&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ba24f6bd-817d-4c29-8901-a40467d24211&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/95fc2a36-bd9c-4f28-8410-ecfa29b6b1db&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/95fc2a36-bd9c-4f28-8410-ecfa29b6b1db&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d83ad4eb-2465-41b0-9148-9e84ba384c88&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d83ad4eb-2465-41b0-9148-9e84ba384c88&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
